Assignment IV – CI/CD Deployment using GitHub & Render (DSO101)
Deploy Your First Web Application using GitHub, GitHub Actions, and Render

Objective
The objective of this assignment was to understand the basics of:
-Git and GitHub version control system
-Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment (CI/CD) using GitHub Actions
-Deployment of a web application using Render.com
The task focused on building a simple web application and automating its deployment pipeline.

Tools & Technologies Used
Git & GitHub (Source control management)
GitHub Actions (CI/CD automation)
Render.com (Cloud deployment platform)
Flask (Python web framework) / or Static HTML (based on implementation)

Project Description
A simple web application was developed and deployed successfully. The application follows a minimal structure and demonstrates a working CI/CD pipeline.
